      • getKey

        public String getKey()
        Description copied from interface: EndpointBinder
        Returns the "key" for this EndpointBinder. The key is the first part of the tuple in an Event. For example, the key for the SpringMVC binder is "springmvc".
        Returns:
        The first part of the tuple in an Event
